{"type": "article", "id": 10712, "title": "Mush-Lume 蘑菇灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-12T06:48:55Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052359515Ey4VgOeqfvlWPij.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span><span>Danielle\r\nTrofe </span></span><span>是从事家居用品的设计师，这次展出的作品是一个蘑菇灯，嗯真的是蘑菇做的灯。利用独特的的原料科学，将玉米秸秆和种子壳这种废弃材料放进含有液体菌丝的模具，“长”出不同形状不同纹路的灯罩，这种环保材料自带磨砂效果，还可以在上面手绘，哪天不想要了扔到花园里就可以让它自己分解，同时给那块土地带来养分。灯罩以外是木质的主体和混凝土底座，几近纯天然。目前 <span>Danielle Trofe </span></span><span>正在积极推动这种材料应用到更广的范围中。<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235948UeBLkAWvXtclVmfH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66704545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235948WEeDChPzFuRK07n9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66704545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523594969vITblohUQ3ySW0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66704545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235949PFqM2NGOzavS4shb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66704545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052359508FMbQTnG6W0JXhZK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66704545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235950aGBFL4jNAqJEu72P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66704545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span></span></span>\r\n</p>\n\n"}